## 第六板块：Lefthook 本地门禁

> 来源：engineering-practices.md §1.3，与 TRAINING.md 公共。

### 预生成配置

`ae init` 默认生成 `lefthook.yml`，包含 **6 道门**（按语言自适应）：

```yaml
# lefthook.yml（由 init 自动生成，按 language 自适应）
pre-commit:
  parallel: true
  commands:
    lint:
      glob: "*.{ts,tsx,js,jsx}"
      run: npx eslint {staged_files}
      stage_fixed: true
    format:
      glob: "*.{ts,tsx,js,jsx,json,md}"
      run: npx prettier --write {staged_files}
      stage_fixed: true
    test-unit:
      run: pnpm vitest run --changed

pre-push:
  commands:
    type-check:
      run: npx tsc --noEmit
    test:
      run: pnpm test
    coverage:
      run: pnpm test:coverage
```

### 激活命令

```bash
# ae init 生成 lefthook.yml 后，需要手动激活（一次性）
$ lefthook install
```

### Python 项目变体

```yaml
pre-commit:
  parallel: true
  commands:
    lint:
      glob: "*.py"
      run: uv run ruff check --fix {staged_files}
      stage_fixed: true
    format:
      glob: "*.py"
      run: uv run ruff format {staged_files}
      stage_fixed: true
    test-unit:
      run: uv run pytest tests/unit -q

pre-push:
  commands:
    type-check:
      run: uv run mypy src/
    test:
      run: uv run pytest
    coverage:
      run: uv run pytest --cov=src --cov-fail-under=80
```

