## 第七板块：CI 云端门禁（7 道门）

> 来源：engineering-practices.md §1 + TRAINING.md 公共。

### 7 道门流水线

```
Gate 0: semgrep ci          安全红线 🛑
Gate 1: lint                代码规范 🤖
Gate 2: type-check          类型检查 🤖
Gate 3: contract-diff       契约一致性 🤖
Gate 4: test                全量测试 🤖
Gate 5: coverage ≥80%       覆盖率 🛑
Gate 6: build               构建验证 🤖
```

Gate 0-4 和 Gate 6 由确定性工具自动判定，不消耗 LLM Token。

### GitHub Actions 模板

`ae init` 默认生成 `.github/workflows/ci.yml`，包含 7 道门：

```yaml
name: CI
on: [push, pull_request]
jobs:
  ci:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v4
      - uses: actions/setup-node@v4
        with: { node-version: 22 }
      - run: npm ci

      # Gate 0: semgrep
      - uses: returntocorp/semgrep-action@v1

      # Gate 1: lint
      - run: npm run lint

      # Gate 2: type-check
      - run: npm run type-check

      # Gate 4: test
      - run: npm test

      # Gate 5: coverage
      - run: npm run test:coverage

      # Gate 6: build
      - run: npm run build
```

### 防御纵深

```
Agent prompt（软约束）
  → Lefthook（硬约束，本地）
    → CI 7 道门（最终防线，云端，不可绕过）
```

